lines.p:
Jehovah has become King!
With grandeur he is clothed;Jehovah is clothed with strength;He wears it like a belt.
The earth is firmly established;It cannot be moved.
Your throne was firmly established long ago;From eternity you have existed.
The rivers have surged, O Jehovah,The rivers have surged and roared;The rivers keep surging and pounding.
Above the sound of many waters,Mightier than the breaking waves of the sea,Jehovah is majestic in the heights.

Your reminders are very trustworthy.
Holiness adorns your house, O Jehovah, for all times.
